WeRec is a simple still effective tool to record incoming and outgoing calls. It grants unlimited recording time of a single or group call. Easy usage makes this app a perfect solution for unpredictable situations when you need to record a call urgently or spontaneously. 

Features: 
- Smart calls' recording; 
- Easy switch-on; 
- Separate library for created files; 
- Intuitive interface;
- Various sharing options; 
- Simple transfer to messengers and social networks; 
- Favourite and Bookmarks sections; 
- Integrated Contacts. 

Having WeRec installed on the phone gives you confidence that important conversations will be preserved at the right moment. Having a personal or business call, you will not miss a detail any more! 
Please, before using the application make sure voice recording is legal in your country. 

With WeRec Premium Plan you get unlimited access to all features WeRec has in stock.

Acquiring of Premium access will allow you:
- Unlimited incoming and outgoing recordings
- No Ads

